Kabutozuka Kofun (Kyoto), sendou-2.jpg|Corridor (towards the entrance)
Kabutozuka Kofun (Kyoto), sendou-1.jpg|Corridor (towards the main chamber)
Kabutozuka Kofun (Kyoto), funkyu.jpg|The Kofun
</gallery>

